Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,- Matsumoto "I'm glad."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Itao "He says it was very good."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guy in red clothes - "Let's get down to business. All these actors and dancers weren't cheap."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Itao "Yeah, That's true."
